<p>Ooo this is a very good question, I approve of this question.</p>
If I went evil, I would
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">do&nbsp;very&nbsp;little,&nbsp;really.</a></div>
